title: CNK Crosses Above Key Moving Average Level - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Wednesday, shares of Cinemark Holdings Inc (Symbol: CNK) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $38.84, changing hands as high as $38.96 per share. Cinemark Holdings Inc shares are currently trading up about 2.5% on the day. The chart below shows the one year performance of CNK shares, versus its 200 day moving average:     Looking at the chart above, CNK's low point in its 52 week range is $34.49 per share, with $43.51 as the 52 week high point - that compares with a last trade of $38.93.
